{%- comment -%}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CUSTOM PAYMENT ICONS
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Custom addition (not part of Impact core). Replaces the "Payment icons" block of the Buy Box app so the app can be
uninstalled. Uses shop.enabled_payment_types, the same source the theme already uses in the footer and the cart, so the
icons always reflect the payment methods actually enabled on the store.

********************************************
Supported variables
********************************************

* block: the section block holding the settings (required)
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- if shop.enabled_payment_types.size > 0 -%}
  <div class="custom-payment-icons" style="
    --cpi-icon-size: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    --cpi-gap: {{ block.settings.min_gap }}px;
    --cpi-alignment: {{ block.settings.alignment }};
    --cpi-max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }};
    --cpi-margin-top: {{ block.settings.margin_top }}px;
    --cpi-margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.margin_bottom }}px;
  " {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
    {%- for type in shop.enabled_payment_types -%}
      {{- type | payment_type_svg_tag -}}
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
{%- endif -%}
